{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "陆小凤乘坐老狐狸的海船出海，牛肉汤也在船上负责做饭。岳洋一直不露面，夜间陆小凤被人打落海中，怀疑是岳洋所为。老狐狸的船因忘记装水而返航，陆小凤在岸边遇到胡生，胡生跃入海中后离奇死亡。陆小凤与牛肉汤在洗澡时发生亲密接触。船再次出海三日后遭遇暴风雨，陆小凤与岳洋对话中得知岳洋早知船会沉，最终船被巨浪打碎沉没。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_shou",
      "speaker_name": "水手",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "起锚！",
      "tone": "嘹亮",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_shou",
      "speaker_name": "水手",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "扬帆！",
      "tone": "嘹亮",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_shou",
      "speaker_name": "水手",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "顺风！",
      "tone": "嘹亮",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你怎么会上船来的？",
      "tone": "吃惊",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为你们上船来了。",
      "tone": "俏皮",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我们上了船，你就要上船了？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我问你，你们在船上，是不是也一样要吃饭？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我就是煮饭的，不但烧饭，还煮牛肉。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你什么时候改行的？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我本来就是烧饭的，只不过偶尔改行做做别的事而已！",
      "tone": "狡黠",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "听说乘坐这条船的，都是很有身份的人。",
      "tone": "闲聊",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "这点我倒能想得到，否则怎么付得起老狐狸的船钱。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你有没有身份？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "没有！",
      "tone": "干脆",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你只有钱？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "也没有，付了船钱后，我就已几乎完全破产。",
      "tone": "坦白",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "没有钱也没关系，如果你偶尔又吃错了药，我还是可以偶尔再改一次行的。",
      "tone": "暧昧",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这间房就是你的，只吃鸡蛋的那个混蛋住在右面第一间。",
      "tone": "介绍",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我能不能换一间？",
      "tone": "请求",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不能！",
      "tone": "果断",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为别的房里都已住着人。",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "那老狐狸劝我把这条船包下来，可是现在每间房里都有人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不但这里八间房全都有人，下面十六间也全都有人，老狐狸一向喜欢热闹，人越多他越高兴。",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只不过住在这上面的才是贵客，老狐狸还特地叫我为你们烧几样好菜，今天晚上你想吃什么？",
      "tone": "热情",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "我想吃烤狐狸，烤得骨头都酥了的老狐狸。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我外婆常说，要得到男人的心，就得先打通他的肠胃，只有会烧一手好菜的女人，才能嫁得到好丈夫。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我们到处找你，你一个人溜到这里来干什么？",
      "tone": "大叫",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "text": "我受不了牛肉汤做的那些菜，想来钓几条鱼下酒。",
      "tone": "悠然",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你钓到几条？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "text": "鱼虽然没钓着，却钓着条老狐狸。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "text": "你们明明已出海，又回来干什么？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我也是回来钓鱼的。",
      "tone": "狡黠",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "text": "那边海上没有鱼？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那边虽然也有鱼，却没有一条肯付我五百两船钱的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "text": "我这条鱼也不肯付的，我上次已经付过了。",
      "tone": "抗议",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "上次是上次，这次是这次，上次是你自己要走的，我又没有把你推下去，所以这次若是还想上船，就得再付我五百两！",
      "tone": "无赖",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "text": "你这人的心究竟有多黑？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只不过比你钓起来的那条狐狸黑一点。",
      "tone": "悠然",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "你好。",
      "tone": "故意",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你好！",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "你是不是在奇怪，我们为什么又回来了？",
      "tone": "试探",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "我们回来找你的。",
      "tone": "直接",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么找我？",
      "tone": "警惕",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "因为你要运的那批货太重，我们怕翻船，只有回来退给你！",
      "tone": "刺探",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "胡生",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "货不是我的，船也不是你的，这件事跟你和我都没有关系，你找我干什么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_hu_sheng",
      "text": "如果货不是你的，你是到这里来干什么的？特地来用鸡鸣五更返魂香对付你的兄弟？",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "奇怪吧？我们居然又碰面了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我奇怪的只不过是连十个蛋你都吃不完。",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "所以你下次若还想打我落水时，最好记住一件事。",
      "tone": "提醒",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "我不喜欢吃白水煮蛋，我喜欢黄酒牛肉。",
      "tone": "幽默",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "下次你再落水时，恐怕已只有一样东西可吃。",
      "tone": "威胁",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "什么东西？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你自己的肉。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "渔人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个人不是被淹死的。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "渔人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他肚子里还没有水。",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是怎么死的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "他死得好像跟那个独眼老头子差不多。",
      "tone": "观察",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "牛肉汤！",
      "tone": "叫喊",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "想不到你这人还满喜欢干净的，居然还会自己来洗澡。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "不自己来洗，难道还去找个人抱着洗？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是不是为了想偷看我洗澡，才来洗澡的？",
      "tone": "调情",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "喜欢偷看别人洗澡的，好像并不是我。",
      "tone": "反击",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我可以偷看你，你可不能偷看我——",
      "tone": "霸道",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你实在不是好东西。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_rou_tang",
      "speaker_name": "牛肉汤",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我好像也不是！",
      "tone": "自嘲",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_shou",
      "speaker_name": "水手",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "开船了，开船了！",
      "tone": "高呼",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他们那里虽然也有人刻佛像，却没有这么好的手艺。",
      "tone": "解释",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "text": "这条船还捱得过去？",
      "tone": "担忧",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_hu_li",
      "speaker_name": "老狐狸",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你最好想法子抓住一块木板。",
      "tone": "绝望",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yue_yang",
      "speaker_name": "岳洋",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你现在总该知道，我为什么一定不让你坐这条船了吧？",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_yue_yang",
      "text": "难道你早就知道这条船要沉？",
      "tone": "震惊",
      "chapter": 3
    }
  ],
  "new_entities": {
    "characters": [
      {
        "id": "char_yu_ren",
        "name": "渔人",
        "alias": [],
        "identity": "海边渔人",
        "faction": null,
